\f4\fs21 \cf5 \cb6 \strokec5 [SEVERITY: HIGH] System: DarkEpilogueScene \'97 Issue: Missing cleanup `SMOKE_POOL.length=0; EX_POOL.length=0;` inside the scene before transitioning out. \'97 Fix: Add cleanup arrays to the Z-key exit logic before starting WorldMap or Title.\
[SEVERITY: MED] System: DarkEpilogueScene \'97 Issue: `_mandelaFlash(self)` delayed call at t=12000ms can trigger after a premature scene transition if the player skips early. \'97 Fix: Wrap the internal logic in an `if(!self._done)` flag guard.\
[SEVERITY: LOW] System: DarkEpilogueScene \'97 Issue: Tween-animated text objects (`mainTxt`, `bigTxt`, `subTxt`) could potentially leak if not explicitly destroyed, though Phaser cleans up on scene exit. \'97 Fix: Destroy the text objects in the `onComplete` tween callbacks. Ensure `setScrollFactor(0)` and `setDepth()` are applied.\
[SEVERITY: HIGH] System: DarkEpilogueScene \'97 Issue: `this.keys.z` is missing proper initialization in `create`, and the `this._done` guard isn't checked before accepting Z input in `update`. \'97 Fix: Add `this.keys = \{z: this.input.keyboard.addKey('Z')\}` and use `if (!this._done && Phaser.Input.Keyboard.JustDown(this.keys.z))`.\
[SEVERITY: MED] System: _drawAnomalyOverlay \'97 Issue: `scene._anomalyTimer = (scene._anomalyTimer||0) - 16` incorrectly assumes a locked 60fps delta, leading to timer drift on varying framerates. \'97 Fix: Modify the function to accept `delta` as a parameter and subtract it dynamically.\
[SEVERITY: HIGH] System: _drawAnomalyOverlay \'97 Issue: `scene.anomalyG.clear()` is only called if `mandela >= 10`. If mandela drops or the condition toggles, the old graphical rectangles will persist on the overlay forever. \'97 Fix: Move `if(scene.anomalyG) scene.anomalyG.clear();` above the conditional blocks.\
[SEVERITY: LOW] System: _drawAnomalyOverlay \'97 Issue: Self-destroying tweens lack `try/catch` wrappers. If the scene changes mid-tween, `txt.destroy()` will crash. \'97 Fix: Wrap `txt.destroy()` inside `try \{ txt.destroy(); \} catch(e) \{\}`.\
[SEVERITY: HIGH] System: _drawAnomalyOverlay \'97 Issue: References `scene.mapOffX` and `scene.tW`, but `mapOffX` is undefined in `WorldMapScene` and `WorldMap2Scene` (they use `scene.offX`). \'97 Fix: Add fallback variables `var ox = scene.mapOffX || scene.offX || 0;` and `var oy = scene.mapOffY || scene.offY || 0;`.\
[SEVERITY: HIGH] System: Level63/64 onUpdate hooks \'97 Issue: Physics object referenced as `scene.edPx.x`, but the level factory uses `scene.ep.x`. Will throw undefined error. \'97 Fix: Change the reference to `scene.ep ? scene.ep.x : 0`.\
[SEVERITY: LOW] System: Level63/64 onUpdate hooks \'97 Issue: `if(!scene._rbFlags)scene._rbFlags=\{\}` is an unnecessary initialization check running every frame. \'97 Fix: Initialize `scene._rbFlags=\{\}` once in the `onCreate` factory hook instead.\
